Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.61,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Chidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:21.38,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Gì?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:30.16,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Có gì đó không ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.36,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.36,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Chidori ấy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.93,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,có ai đang đe doạ cô ấy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.36,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Hay là do lạm dụng thuốc?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.40,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Khó nói lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.86,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.47,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Hôm nay có việc, nên tớ sẽ về sớm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.91,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.14,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Chidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.11,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.97,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,À... cô có chuyện gì phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.27,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Nếu cô gặp rắc rối tôi sẽ giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.95,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Kh-không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:14:00.68,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Tôi ổn mà. Đừng lo. Chào!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.38,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Chuyện này thật phiền. Tôi thấy lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.76,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Này, Sagara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.49,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Chủ nhật này cậu có rảnh không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.20,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Tôi có thể sắp xếp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.44,Standard (FMP),,0000,0000,0000,,Vậy, cậu có muốn đi đâu đó không?
